thread.title: Joy Fulford

author: Joy Fulford
title: Joy Fulford
text: I found tonerprice.com through google and was a little hesitant because the prices were so low. I was shocked that my first order arrived the next day and was exactly what I needed. The prices cant be beat, the site is easy to navigate and shipping is FAST (at least for me). I now use the site for all of my toner needs for an entire office and have saved a ton of money. Definitely use them.
